 *
 * @code
 *
 * culite::dns::RdVector Xd; // double precision real vector
 * culite::dns::RfVector Xs; // single precision real vector
 * culite::dns::CdVector Xz; // double precision complex vector
 * culite::dns::CfVector Xc; // single precision complex vector
